name: Aura prismal
description:
This is a collaboration between @BarbaraBezina and @silviamaria (Twitter)

I feel anxious and my feelings go beyond the limits of my body. 
I feel filled with white light and I turn it into colors.
I wait for an inner strength that never seems to come.
But now I know that that inner strength inhabits me.
My aura has the color of my fears, of my lack of control. 
And it also has the color of my joy and my confidence.
Sometimes I want to be another version of myself.
And I know that I can become who I want to be.
Sometimes I want to leave my body and fly away with my soul.
And I do it every night and bring with me gifts from other worlds.

Photography + traditional painting
